n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>\n  <em>Tema</em>\n  </td><td>\n  2×1 Emprender y no morir en el intento y Podcasting para principiantes\n  </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Comunidad</em>\n  </td><td>   <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/WordPress-Madrid/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Comunidad:&nbsp;WordPress Madrid</a>   </td></tr><tr><td>   <em>Hora y localidad</em></td><td>   19:00 | Madrid (Spain)   </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Espacio</em>\n  </td><td>\n  <em>Google For Startups Campus</em>\n  </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Dirección</em>\n  </td><td>\n  <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Calle%20Moreno%20Nieto,%202,28005%20%20Madrid,%20Madrid%20(Spain)/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Calle Moreno Nieto, 2,28005\n  Madrid, Madrid (Spain)</a>\n  </td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Viernes 25 </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>\n  <em>Tema</em>\n  </td><td>\n  Secretos y buenas prácticas para diseño web\n  </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Comunidad</em>\n  </td><td>   <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/es-ES/Alcobendas-WordPress-Meetup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Comunidad:&nbsp;WordPress Alcobendas</a>   </td></tr><tr><td>   <em>Hora y localidad</em></td><td>   19:00 | Alcobendas (Spain)   </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Espacio</em>\n  </td><td>\n  <em>Centro Cultural Pablo Iglesias</em>\n  </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Dirección</em>\n  </td><td>\n  <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Paseo%20de%20la%20Chopera,%20n%C2%BA%2059,%20Alcobendas%20(Spain)/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Paseo de la Chopera, nº 59,\n  Alcobendas (Spain)</a>\n  </td></tr><tr><td>\n  <em>Más reseñas</em>\n  </td><td>\n  <em>Pregunta en el mostrador por el meetup WordPress Alcoben